{"tid":956914,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友唔陪我睇戲","createTime":"2018-12-26T16:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T17:59:02.000Z","uid":220460,"like":450,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"5434984e92d3f469697225a756f8ecb7cec66a6a","tid":956914,"uid":220460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T16:06:36.000Z","msg":"之前成日聽班friend講話比悲傷更悲傷的故事好好睇 搞到我都心思思想去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁梗係搵男朋友睇㗎啦<br />\n佢又不嬲毒撚性格 話唔睇呢啲on9韓劇電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 戲飛又貴 叫我求其搵個friend睇算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 算啦我都唔想逼佢做啲佢唔想做既事 結果一路到而家我都仲未睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係24號嗰日男朋友終於放假 佢就話佢有班friend約佢睇呢套 佢地六個人 四女兩男咁去睇 仲問我俾唔俾<br />\n咁我就梗係好唔甘心啦 反問佢 點解我約佢就唔出 一有friend約就即刻應承 佢就話佢都唔係好想睇 但係因為好耐無見過班friend所以就去睇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然好唔開心 但係唔俾佢去睇又好似好衰所以都係無出聲<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"596f30b5c5c7d0cde0f154cfcba6a892ba4c8ba3","tid":956914,"uid":95542,"like":140,"dislike":4,"score":136,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T16:07:40.000Z","msg":"我陪你"},{"pid":"a6316e4f4942e2b0874ac7d5797d3c261ff30d67","tid":956914,"uid":199274,"like":139,"dislike":3,"score":136,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T16:07:58.000Z","msg":"放棄佢！搵我...咩都可以陪你做"},{"pid":"83a7021fe1fbacd3a3fec83664cff438e746d13a","tid":956914,"uid":828,"like":105,"dislike":3,"score":102,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T16:08:27.000Z","msg":"你都去睇咪得"},{"pid":"3f30d4ef74f1c011e0db8528c0ca16987408f86b","tid":956914,"uid":73114,"like":4,"dislike":16,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T16:09:07.000Z","msg":"做我條囡啦<br />\n我陪你睇十次都duck"},{"pid":"c102d6c896aa1178d9f77b11ff880d4635951628","tid":956914,"uid":7734,"like":450,"dislike":5,"score":445,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T16:09:57.000Z","msg":"係錫你嘅唔想睇都會陪你睇<br />\n講到咁唔想睇轉個頭又陪friend睇 垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f0239fd79b8ecdb5c6462dd4d73658c9a132965","tid":956914,"uid":150739,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T16:10:15.000Z","msg":"叫佢另約時間囉<br />\n或者淨係食餐飯唔睇戲"},{"pid":"6fc027a990d9af58a4ffa65439bc08ffd73adef5","tid":956914,"uid":624,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T16:10:16.000Z","msg":"比呢個post佢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你唔講比佢知 佢又點會知你點諗呢？"},{"pid":"fa78d4dd501aa7ccace7c32fb562a22845a34505","tid":956914,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T16:10:57.000Z","msg":"飛"},{"pid":"65cc9eddbc9aac31d1c95d55a167da9bbdf48d48","tid":956914,"uid":34714,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T16:11:12.000Z","msg":"呢套好似台灣野"},{"pid":"8d1dc4a731c8a603cad8186f4381bac704231ba8","tid":956914,"uid":109655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T16:18:28.000Z","msg":"分手 你要睇咩我都可以陪你<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb08c089da4be514f9db0a7f51fb2de2c7dddbec","tid":956914,"uid":220460,"like":2,"dislike":40,"score":-38,"quote":{"pid":"83a7021fe1fbacd3a3fec83664cff438e746d13a","tid":956914,"uid":828,"like":105,"dislike":3,"score":102,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T16:08:27.000Z","msg":"你都去睇咪得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T16:18:30.000Z","msg":"我試過話想去佢同佢班friend既聚會 男朋友都表示無問題 但係佢班friend好似唔太喜我我係度咁 我一嚟佢地就走 得返我同男朋友係度<img src=\"/a